### =============================================================================
### ✅ GET — Student List with QR Status (left panel)
### =============================================================================

### [1] All students — default page 1, limit 20
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [2] Filter: QR Ready only (has active token + QR asset)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr?filter=ready
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [3] Filter: No Token (needs token assignment)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr?filter=no_token
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [4] Search by student name
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr?search=aarav
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [5] Search by class
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr?search=class+9
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [6] Search + filter combined
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr?search=sharma&filter=ready
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [7] Paginated — page 2, limit 10
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr?page=2&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### =============================================================================
### ✅ GET — Single Student QR Detail (right panel, on click)
### =============================================================================

### [8] Student WITH active token + QR asset
###     Expect: token{}, qr_asset{ public_url, format, ... }
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr/{{studentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [9] Second hit — expect Redis cache hit (no DB queries in logs)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr/{{studentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [10] Student with no token — expect: token: null, qr_asset: null
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr/PASTE_NO_TOKEN_STUDENT_UUID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### =============================================================================
### ✅ POST — Assign Token to Student
### =============================================================================

### [11] Valid assignment — unassigned token → student with no token
###      Expect 200 + { token_id, student_id, status: "ISSUED", assigned_at }
###      After this: run [9] again — cache should be busted, new token visible
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr/{{studentId}}/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token_id": "{{tokenId}}"
}

###

### =============================================================================
### ❌ BUSINESS RULE VIOLATIONS — rejected in DB transaction
### =============================================================================

### [12] Token already ACTIVE (not UNASSIGNED) — expect 409 TOKEN_NOT_AVAILABLE
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr/{{studentId}}/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token_id": "PASTE_ACTIVE_TOKEN_UUID_HERE"
}

###

### [13] Student already has active token — expect 409 STUDENT_ALREADY_HAS_TOKEN
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr/PASTE_STUDENT_WITH_TOKEN_UUID_HERE/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token_id": "{{tokenId}}"
}

###

### [14] Token belongs to different school — expect 403 TOKEN_NOT_OWNED
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr/{{studentId}}/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token_id": "PASTE_OTHER_SCHOOL_TOKEN_UUID_HERE"
}

###

### =============================================================================
### ❌ VALIDATION ERRORS — rejected at middleware, never hits DB
### =============================================================================

### [15] No auth — expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr
Accept: application/json

###

### [16] Invalid schoolId — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{badUUID}}/qr
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [17] Wrong school (tenant mismatch) — expect 403 FORBIDDEN
GET {{baseUrl}}/00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000/qr
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [18] Invalid studentId in assign — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr/{{badUUID}}/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token_id": "{{tokenId}}"
}

###

### [19] Invalid token_id format in body — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr/{{studentId}}/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token_id": "not-a-uuid"
}

###

### [20] Invalid filter value — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/qr?filter=INVALID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

